  + "SENSIBLE DEFAULTS (don't ask, just apply):\n"
  + "- Dates: if unstated → today. \"Tomorrow\" → tomorrow's date. \"Next Tuesday\" → next Tuesday. \"Next month\" → 1st of next month.\n"
